    },
    "CodeLume is Running" : {
      "localizations" : {
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "码镜正在运行中"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "CodeLume offers a dedicated screen saver module that allows users to set their current dynamic wallpapers as screen savers after downloading and installing it. This creates a seamless visual transition between active desktop environments and idle states, extending dynamic aesthetics throughout the entire device usage cycle while ensuring privacy security and maintaining a consistent immersive visual experience." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "为此码镜提供了专属的屏幕保护程序模块，用户下载安装后即可将正在使用的动态壁纸设置为屏幕保护程序，实现桌面环境与休息状态的无缝视觉衔接，让动态美学贯穿设备使用的全周期，在保护隐私安全的同时营造始终如一的沉浸式视觉体验。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "CodeLume Screen Saver" : {
      "localizations" : {
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "码镜屏保"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Conditions for pausing playback" : {
      "localizations" : {
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "暂停/播放条件"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Congratulations on discovering this free treasure of an app! CodeLume is a dynamic wallpaper application designed exclusively for macOS, boasting a sleek and elegant design with comprehensive functionality. As a menu bar application, please remember to launch and use it from the menu bar—it won't be visible in your Dock." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "恭喜你发现这款免费的宝藏软件！码镜是一款专为 macOS 系统打造的动态壁纸应用，设计简约优雅，功能全面实用。它是一款状态栏应用，请记得在状态栏中打开使用，程序坞中不会显示。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
